<view class="v-top">
    <view class="v-one">购买此产品，订单完成后即可获得</view>
    <view class="v-two">【¥20代金抵用券】</view>
</view>
<swiper class='swiper' indicator-dots='true' autoplay='true' interval='5000' duration='1000' circular='true' indicator-dots="{{color}}" indicator-active-color="{{activeColor}}">
    <block wx:for="{{images}}" wx:for-index="index">
        <swiper-item>
            <image src='{{item.url}}' class='u-img-slide' mode='aspectFill'></image>
        </swiper-item>
    </block>
</swiper>
<view class="goods-info">
    <view class="goods-box">
        <view class="goodsbox-p">
            ￥
            <text>45-58</text>
            /500g
        </view>
        <view class="goodsbox-ul">
            <view>满减用券</view>
            <view>代金券抵用</view>
        </view>
        <view class="goods-title">时尚水果店 新鲜草莓 爽甜口口 美味不止一夏天</view>
        <view class="share"><image src="/static/images/share.png" />分享</view>
    </view>
</view>
<view class="goods-mes">
    <view class="goodsmes-t">购买详情</view>
    <view class="goods-total">
        <view class="goodst-div">
            <image src="/static/images/pr.png" />
            <view>￥52/500g</view>
        </view>
        <view class="goodst-div">
            <image src="/static/images/add3.png" />
            <view>湖南·长沙·芙蓉区</view>
        </view>
        <view class="goodst-div">
            <image src="/static/images/kg.png" />
            <view>质量（mass）是量度物体惯性大小的物理量。中，质量的基本单位是千克（符号Kg）</view>
        </view>
    </view>
</view>
<!-- 底部栏 -->
<view class="goods-bottom">
    <view class="goodsbot-left">
        <view class="goodsbot-left-view">
            <view style="color: #E24500;font-weight: 600;">
                实付￥
                <text style="font-size: 22px;">32.00</text>
                
            </view>
            <view style="color: #666666;">
                代金券抵用￥
                <text>20</text>
            </view>
        </view>
        <view class="goods-ticket">限时抵券</view>
    </view>
    <view class="goods-btn">立即购买</view>
</view>